{"tid":307048,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老蘭男女飛凳大混戰心口撞心口","createTime":"2017-07-03T04:54:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T06:03:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"94d27ad3c7fd4635fa0036de76e30d20bf4c7bb8","tid":307048,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T04:54:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20077508&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170703\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20077508%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170703&d=PG5mdWBhha%2BgT1dk288bntZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=67cee7bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20077508%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170703&h=7de2ddc1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20077508&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170703</a><br />\n<br />\n老蘭男女飛凳大混戰<br />\n心口撞心口<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中環蘭桂坊昨凌晨發生集體打鬥事件。讀者毛先生，昨凌晨約3時半，往蘭桂坊的酒吧消遣，其間聽得斜路上傳來嘈吵聲，循聲望去，赫見有多名不同國籍的男女互相推撞，「心口撞心口」，未幾即互相揮拳毆鬥，並打入酒吧內，「七國咁亂、好恐怖」，他見情況不能受控，遂自行離去是非地帶，並揚言以後會減少往上址，「真係可免則免」。<br />\n由毛先生拍得的影片可見，雖然是深宵時分，但蘭桂坊仍人頭湧湧，期間為數逾15名男女，在斜路上互相推撞及追打，有人揮拳踢腿，亦有人揮舞膠凳扑向對方，不少人士一度倒地，要旁人攙扶起身，情況混亂。<br />\n警方發言人指，昨凌晨3時許，一名18歲菲律賓籍男子，報稱與友人往上址消遣期間，疑因身體碰撞問題，遭4名外籍男子追打，其後對方逃去無蹤。事主頭及手受傷，需送院治理。現案件交由中區警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n97年主權移交至今，香港前進還是倒退？「蘋果」與你細數廿載風雨。<br />\n【回歸二十年】專頁：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhksar20.appledaily.com.hk&d=PG5mdWBhha%2BgT1dk288bntZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=a96af58a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk</a>￼"},{"pid":"385606fa0220ff15635ef28552b70c346c5a48ab","tid":307048,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T04:56:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c10a0f57be7a101d905361c010959e241e721f3","tid":307048,"uid":113074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T04:57:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>場內消息<br />\n賓仔抽水</blockquote><br />\n雞都要揀客"},{"pid":"7461e8ed92a543061578722385c402f454042776","tid":307048,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T06:03:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>場內消息<br />\n賓仔抽水</blockquote><br />\n係人都知d啡色人種極度咸濕"}]}